Ahoy!
Welcome aboard
the good ship
Navigable!

Navigable is an opinionated extension of Hanami::Router that automatically connects restful routes to Command objects. When a Navigable application starts, it loads all the files in the commands folder, and registers a corresponding route for each command class.

Note: To remove this splash screen, define a root command at `commands/root.rb`.

Navigable version: <%= Navigable::VERSION %> | Ruby version: <%= RUBY_VERSION %>
